# Final Message

If there's one thing to remember from this entire journey, let it be this:

> History is not the story of extraordinary people doing extraordinary things.

It is the story of ordinary people trying to solve the problems they inherited.

Sometimes they succeeded.

Sometimes they failed.

Often, they created new problems for future generations.

And those generations tried again.

You are one of those generations.

The world you inherited was shaped by countless human choices.

The world that comes next will be shaped by yours.

**Congratulations.**

**You didn't just finish learning history.**

**You learned how to see it.**
